This interface is for objects which want to declare that they have a publicly editable aspect.

getEditor

public Editor getEditor()
Get an Editor for this object. Changes to the editor should end up reflected as changes to this object, and changes to this object should end up reflected as changes to the editor.

Returns:
an Editor for this object
